Feature of the game: Stars in the Trash (Official Trailer) - New PC / Steam / PS4 Games Announcement Trailer

Stars in the Trash (Official Trailer) - New PC / Steam / PS4 Games Announcement Trailer

Have you ever wanted to be a cat?, you will be able, thanks to the aventure platformer The Purring Quest. Take on the role of Kimchi the cat and meet famous cats of the internet in a journey full of humor. Enjoy the detailed hand drawn graphics and the smooth animations made by a veteran traditional animator with experience in major studies like Disney and Warner. A percentage of the profits will go directly to various animal welfare associations. So in addition to enjoying the game, you are contributing to a good cause. (source: valhallacats.com)
